subject: College Athletics
Amateur Athletics
Wrestling
lead_paragraph: Ohio State earned semifinal berths in 4 of 10 weight classes, vaulting past Iowa State and Iowa to take the lead at the N.C.A.A. wrestling championships in St. Louis. Ohio State had 61.5 points for a 4-point lead over Iowa State. wrestling.
